Take this kiss upon the brow
And in parting from you now
Thus much let me avow
You are not wrong, who deem
That my days have been a dream
Yet if hope has flown away
In a night or in a day
In a vision or in none
Is it therefore the less gone
All that we see or seem
All that we see or seem
Is but a dream within a dream

I stand amid the roar
Of a surf tormented shore
And I hold within my hands
Grains of the golden sand
Oh how they creep
Through my fingers to the deep
While I weep while I weep
Oh God can I not grasp
Them with a tighter clasp
Oh God can I not save
One from the pitiless wave
Is all that we see or seem
Is all that we see or seem
But a dream within a dream
Dream, dream, dream ...

girl and guy were speeding over 100 mph on the road on a motorcycle...

Girl: Slow down. Im scared.
Guy: No this is fun.
Girl: No its not. Please, its too scary!
Guy: Then tell me you love me.
Girl: Fine, I love you. Slow down!
Guy: Now give me a BIG hug.
*Girl hugs him*
Guy: Can you take my helmet off & put it on yourself? Its bugging me.

(In the paper the next day):

A motorcycle had crashed into a building because of break failure. 2 people were on it, but only 1 survived. The truth was that halfway down the road, the guy realized that his breaks broke, but he didn't want to let the girl know. Instead, he had her say she loved him & felt her hug one last time, then had her wear his helmet so that she would live even though it meant that he would die.

warning: this isnt me being happy... this is me trying to let something out not to be read, not really careing if it is, maybe wanting it to be read by some but not all, this is only what i would put in my journal in a book but my hand cant write as fast as it types... and i dont wanna loooose my thoughts i want to look back at this...

jesus christ is there any day i get threw with out crying??

im so tired of being sick mentally n physically... i need help or a friend that actually REALLY cares... not only says they do but shows it...

im so incredably close to going back to "ED" i dont know how long i can hold back... its been to long... and im a faliur...

i balled today on maggies back porch cause i couldnt stop thinking about how some one had told me shannon was a foxx n it wasent the first time... n i obsessed over the fact that im so discusting and it was just like wrong timeing i havent felt ok with myself in soo long not since i got my first taste of "meaningless sex"... it makes me not want her to be around me cause ill feel like im the ugliest person in the world when she did nothing besides be perfect... i need help... i keep getting sicker and sicker... but only in my low slopes... when im getting a taste of happyness it freaks people out in a way they love... to bad im only happy half of each day... the other half... feeling only pain... 

i dont know why i cant get over anything... i dont know why every thing is a big deal to me... and when im on drugs im fine... every thing is fine i dont want to end up like my dad... chooseing an addiction over my family then quiting and looking at every thing i had lost... going down the wrong path then trying to go up the rite one realizing that i can never have would i could have.

im fucking crying out loud to people and they think i just want pitty i dont give a shit about pitty i want fucking help... i need help... i need to be helped... and no one is helping me... and i am way past the point where i could help myself...

i picture myself laying in my bed tonight like every other night... numb... face so wet from the tears... and my brain and heart on a one on one fight to the death... just waiting for my mood to swith... waiting for the next swing and hopeing its a good one not a bad one.

i dont remeber why i stopped takeing my meds... and i dont know why  i wont take them... im almost affraid to...

im so scared now... i ust to be possitive, i ust to be happy,  i ust to not care,  i ust to be forgiving, i ust to be giveing, i ust to go to school... i dont knwo why i am not anymore... i dont know whats happening... i only know its gonna get worse and im only scared... 

i need some false happyness... they say you cannot love until you love yourself... i find that complete bull shit... i havent loves myself in years... and ive had several exsperiences in love and i wa shappy for as long as it lasted in each one... ide face anything to be happy... and being liked bye someone i liek is one of the only things that makes ma happy... i could back this up on to as why but i dont really want to...

I dont exspect anyone to write anything back to me... i already know that my pain means nothing to anyone... 

no one understands how much i care about them... but i only show my love if they show me love first that way i wont be the only oe putting it out... what a horrible thing to teach ur self... how completely selfish...
